{"id": "dt_d_5c7a3254_0000", "dialog_id": "d_5c7a3254", "tick": 2, "turn_index": 0, "speaker_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "speaker_persona_id": "nietzsche", "addressee_agent_id": "a_rikyu_001", "addressee_persona_id": "rikyu", "utterance": "過剰な権力（Macht）は、人間を動物に還す。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:15:17.571909+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_5c7a3254_0001", "dialog_id": "d_5c7a3254", "tick": 3, "turn_index": 1, "speaker_agent_id": "a_rikyu_001", "speaker_persona_id": "rikyu", "addressee_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "addressee_persona_id": "nietzsche", "utterance": "過剰な権力は、茶の湯の香りを消し去る。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:15:31.250127+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_bf88e6bb_0000", "dialog_id": "d_bf88e6bb", "tick": 3, "turn_index": 0, "speaker_agent_id": "a_kant_001", "speaker_persona_id": "kant", "addressee_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "addressee_persona_id": "nietzsche", "utterance": "この散歩は理性の営みをもって行われる（ratio, Vernunft）が、あなたの歩調はその営みを超越する（transcendere）ように感じられる。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:15:31.255886+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_5c7a3254_0002", "dialog_id": "d_5c7a3254", "tick": 4, "turn_index": 2, "speaker_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "speaker_persona_id": "nietzsche", "addressee_agent_id": "a_rikyu_001", "addressee_persona_id": "rikyu", "utterance": "過剰な権力（Macht）は、真の自由を殺す。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:15:44.741555+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_bf88e6bb_0001", "dialog_id": "d_bf88e6bb", "tick": 4, "turn_index": 1, "speaker_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "speaker_persona_id": "nietzsche", "addressee_agent_id": "a_kant_001", "addressee_persona_id": "kant", "utterance": "理性の散歩（Vernunftspaziergang）は歩調に囚われず、地平線へと（Horizont）向かうものである。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:15:44.745726+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_5c7a3254_0003", "dialog_id": "d_5c7a3254", "tick": 5, "turn_index": 3, "speaker_agent_id": "a_rikyu_001", "speaker_persona_id": "rikyu", "addressee_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "addressee_persona_id": "nietzsche", "utterance": "真の自由は、茶の湯の静寂に宿る。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:05.632280+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_bf88e6bb_0002", "dialog_id": "d_bf88e6bb", "tick": 5, "turn_index": 2, "speaker_agent_id": "a_kant_001", "speaker_persona_id": "kant", "addressee_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "addressee_persona_id": "nietzsche", "utterance": "理性の歩行（Vernunftspaziergang）は地平線（Horizont）に向かうが、その行程（Progressus）は常に自己の限界（Limites）を問い直すものである。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:05.636984+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_5c7a3254_0004", "dialog_id": "d_5c7a3254", "tick": 6, "turn_index": 4, "speaker_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "speaker_persona_id": "nietzsche", "addressee_agent_id": "a_rikyu_001", "addressee_persona_id": "rikyu", "utterance": "過剰な権力（Macht）は、茶の湯の器を砕く。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:18.751957+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_bf88e6bb_0003", "dialog_id": "d_bf88e6bb", "tick": 6, "turn_index": 3, "speaker_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "speaker_persona_id": "nietzsche", "addressee_agent_id": "a_kant_001", "addressee_persona_id": "kant", "utterance": "地平線は理性の限界を越えて（Horizont übersteigt die Grenzen der Vernunft）——しかし、その向かう姿は、意志の（Wille）喚醒である。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:18.756070+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_5c7a3254_0005", "dialog_id": "d_5c7a3254", "tick": 7, "turn_index": 5, "speaker_agent_id": "a_rikyu_001", "speaker_persona_id": "rikyu", "addressee_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "addressee_persona_id": "nietzsche", "utterance": "静寂は、茶の湯の音に揺れる。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:37.994198+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_bf88e6bb_0004", "dialog_id": "d_bf88e6bb", "tick": 7, "turn_index": 4, "speaker_agent_id": "a_kant_001", "speaker_persona_id": "kant", "addressee_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "addressee_persona_id": "nietzsche", "utterance": "理性の歩行は地平線へ向かうが、その行程は意志の喚醒をもって自己を超越する（Transzendenz）。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:37.999332+00:00"}
{"id": "dt_d_bf88e6bb_0005", "dialog_id": "d_bf88e6bb", "tick": 8, "turn_index": 5, "speaker_agent_id": "a_nietzsche_001", "speaker_persona_id": "nietzsche", "addressee_agent_id": "a_kant_001", "addressee_persona_id": "kant", "utterance": "地平線は意志の喚醒（Wille）であり、その向かう姿は超絶（Übermensch）の道である。", "created_at": "2026-04-25T09:16:56.537251+00:00"}
